snippet.title: 10SIX (テンシックス) - Sega Dreamcast (UNRELEASED)
snippet.description:
10SIX (テンシックス) is online realtime strategy game by using Heat.net. Porting to Sega Dreamcast has been announced in 2010, but it canceled in March 2011.
Source:
http://web.archive.org/web/*/http://www.sega.com:80/vault/movies/10six_1/10SIX_HI1.wmv
